"The first image that comes to most people's mind is dieting or imprisonment," says Jesse Mecham, founder of the budgeting software You Need A Budget.
Creating a budget can be empowering and forge paths for new opportunities.
"Those moments, where you have the willpower or you have the energy, you have this motivation," Mecham says.
With credit cards and overdraft protections, "We've gotten really used to the idea that we never really run out of money," Mecham says.
You Need A Budget has been a sponsor of NPR in the past.